repository-code: "https://github.com/meeg-lab/research-tracker"
url: "https://meeg-lab.github.io/research-tracker/"
abstract: >-
  A single-file, browser-based tool for tracking research projects as ordered
  pipeline stages, recording the software used at each step, managing milestones,
  and maintaining a searchable literature log with CrossRef DOI lookup. Runs
  entirely client-side with no install, no server, and no data transmission.
